### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/

### List all tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks

### Filter: only open tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks?done=false

### Get a single task
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/1

### Get a task that doesn't exist (expect 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/999

### Create a task (expect 201)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Deploy the API to a free host",
  "priority": "critical"
}

### Create a task with invalid data (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": ""
}

### Update a task (expect 200)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "done": true
}

### Delete a task (expect 204)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/4
